INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(112, 1, '2013-04-30 06:35:29', '2013-04-30 06:35:29', '<h1>Amputation Injury Settlements</h1>\nIf you have suffered injuries from a construction accident, auto accident or any other accident that resulted in amputation or dismemberment, you will need the assistance of an experienced amputation injury lawyer to represent you in your case. The Law Office of David Azizi has extensive experience in the litigation of cases wherein the client has sustained amputation or dismemberment injuries. Amputation accidents can be physically and emotionally devastating as well as leaving you and your family in a state of financial hardship. We specialize in serious personal injury cases and know what it takes litigate cases in order to recover the maximum settlement or verdict possible.\n\n<h2>When to Pursue an Amputation Injury Lawyer</h2>\n\nAny type of accident can be a traumatic experience, but when an amputation is required as a result of someone else’s negligence, you have certain rights that can help you recover compensation for damages sustained. The common types of amputation or dismemberment injuries occur when:\nYou have lost an arm, leg, hand or foot in an auto accident\nYou have lost a limb from a construction accident\nYou have lost a limb as a result of negligence on private or public property\nYou have had to undergo amputation from malpractive by a surgeon\nYou have suffered injuries and a loss of a limb from machines or equipment at work\n\nAn amputation is a form of a catastrophic personal injury and these cases cannot be taken lightly. At the Law Office of David Azizi, we take the time to conduct a full assessment of your case in order to build a solid claim against the offending party.\n\n<h2>Working with an Amputation Injury Lawyer</h2>\n\nWe know how challenging it can be to be responsible for rising medical costs, not being able to return to work or having to manage the emotional repercussions of a traumatic accident. This is why our experienced amputation lawyers will do everything legally possible to investigate your case so that you can receive the compensation you deserve. We will contact witnesses, get in touch with medical professionals and forecast the future costs of managing your medical and healthcare expenses so that we can fight for the appropriate amount of damages for your specific case.\n\nThe team of legal professionals at AziziPersonalInjury.com will not charge you any fees until your case is resolved. We are dedicated to helping you with your claim. Contact us today at (800) 991-LAW2 so that we can provide you with immediate assistance.', 'Amputation Injury', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '110-revision-2', '', '', '2013-04-30 06:35:29', '2013-04-30 06:35:29', '', 110, 'http://azizipersonalinjury.com/dev/espanol/110-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
