INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(241, 1, '2013-04-30 07:16:08', '2013-04-30 07:16:08', '<h1>Brain Injury Lawyers in Los Angeles and California</h1>\r\nIf you or a family member has suffered from a brain injury as a result of an accident or other catastrophic event, you will need the assistance of an experienced personal injury lawyer from the Law Offices of David Azizi to handle the case. The effects of brain injuries can last for years, even decades, and you may be responsible for expensive medical bills, counseling and other health care cost. AzizPersonalInjuyr.com can help you litigate your brain injury case and ensure that you receive the appropriate compensation for damages which you deserve. \r\n\r\n<h3>Why Work with a Brain Injury Lawyer? </h3>\r\n\r\nDealing with traumatic brain injury can be a complicated process, and most health care providers do not have the resources to cover all of the recovery and rehabilitation costs involved. Victims of a brain injury, their families and/or caregivers need specialized legal representation to assist them in litigating a solid case against the offending negligent party. AziziPersonalInjury.com can help you with every stage of this process, and our lawyers have extensive experience in the field to represent your interest vigorously. \r\n\r\n<h3>What are the Symptoms of Brain Injury? </h3>\r\n\r\nMany symptoms of brain injury do not show up for several weeks or months after the initial accident or event, so it is important to recognize the symptoms as soon as they begin to interfere with day-to-day life activities. When brain functions are disrupted, the individual may experience:\r\nDisturbed sleep patterns\r\nSlowed or impaired thinking\r\nDifficulty concentrating\r\nMemory lapses\r\nFaulty judgement\r\nPeriods of depression\r\n\r\n\r\nIn many cases, the individual will need to undergo cognitive and neurological testing to find out how severe the brain injury is, and what parts of the brain have been damaged. \r\n\r\nAll of these effects and the medical care that the individual needs must be taken on by the patient or their families. This financial burden may be reduced with the help of a personal injury attorney from AzizPersonalInjury.com; our firm will do everything possible to keep the client’s best interests in mind, and do the work necessary to build a solid case. \r\n\r\n<h3>How the Law Office of David Azizi Can Assist You with your Brain Injury Case? </h3>\r\n\r\nAt AziziPersonalInjury.com, we offer a free, no obligation initial consultation. If we accept your case, we will not charge you until the case has been resolved. ', 'Brain Injury Lawyers in Los Angeles and California', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '116-revision-5', '', '', '2013-04-30 07:16:08', '2013-04-30 07:16:08', '', 116, 'http://azizipersonalinjury.com/dev/espanol/116-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(242, 1, '2013-05-11 01:46:58', '2013-05-11 01:46:58', '<h1>Heridas Fuero o Explosión</h1>\n\nSi usted ha sufrido de heridas de fuego o explosión a consecuencia de un accidente, usted puede tener derecho a recibir compensación por sus danos del partido negligente. Heridas que son el resultado de un fuego o explosión pueden ser muy grave y requerir cuidado médico intensivo inclusive pero no limitado al tratamiento de dermatólogos y los centros físicos de rehabilitación. Las Oficinas de Ley de David Azizi tiene experiencia extensa en manejar casos de herida de quemadura. \n\n<h3>Casos de Heridade de quemaduras </h3>\n\nNearly 2.4 million burn injuries are reported every year in the United States, and 75,000 of those injuries required hospitalization in the last year. Burn victims not only suffer from the immediate pain but also suffer from many emotional issues as a result of the traumatic experience. A burn injury can be a physically and emotionally devastating experience. These complex cases often require the case to be handled by an experienced personal injury attorney. \n\nSince there are several factors involved in determining the severity of the burn, determining if the injury was a result of negligence as well as finding out if the burns will create lifelong problems for the individual, you will need an experienced and knowledgeable burn injury lawyer to represent you. The Law Offices of David Azizi will take the time to assess your specific case and determine what the best course of action for your case will be. \n\n<h3>Fire Injury and Explosion Injury Cases </h3>\n\nIn addition to sustaining burn injuries from an accident, many people are injured from heat inhalation, systemic toxins in the environment and smoke inhalation. Negligence is the most common reason for fires and explosions. \n\n<h3>How a Burn Injury Lawyer Can Help You? </h3>\n\nAn experienced burn injury attorney from AziziPersonalInjury.com can determine the scope of damages sustained by victims of fire and explosion accidents. We understand that in addition to the physical injuries sustained, a burn victim also suffers from depression, mental anguish, post traumatic disorder and embarrassment. \n\nOur firm will always look out for your best interests and make sure we recover for both your physical and emotional injuries. At AziziPersonalInjury.com, we do not charge you until we recover on your behalf. We are committed to helping you receive compensation from damages from your burn, fire and explosion injury case. Contact us as soon as possible so that we may provide you immediate assistance.', 'Heridas Fuero o Explosión', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '120-autosave', '', '', '2013-05-11 01:46:58', '2013-05-11 01:46:58', '', 120, 'http://azizipersonalinjury.com/dev/espanol/120-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
