INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(259, 1, '2013-04-30 07:08:52', '2013-04-30 07:08:52', '<h1>A Motorcycle Accident Personal Injury Lawyer Can Help You Recover.</h1>\r\nA motorcycle accident can be particularly serious, and you may need both medical care and a motorcycle accident personal injury attorney to get everything back together. Although any motor vehicle accident can cause an injury, those that involve a motorcycle are often much worse and can produce crippling results. The motorcyclist is not usually the one at fault in a motorcycle accident, but not seeing him or her is no excuse for the negligent driver of the other vehicle. \r\n\r\nA motorcycle accident often produces very serious injuries, or even death, and without a personal injury lawyer from AziziPersonalInjury.com, you may not receive full compensation for all your medical expenses, lost wages during your recovery time or beyond, or for less obvious costs such as therapy or even fully restoring your bike. Your distress and pain, while not physical, need to be addressed as well, and this requires a strong and determined attorney to present your case. \r\n\r\nPrompt medical care should always be your first concern after any motorcycle accident. Serious injuries or unconsciousness, however, may prevent you from being able to take the following necessary steps: \r\n\r\n1)	Remain at the scene of the accident until the police have arrived.\r\n2)	File or assist in the preparation of a police report.\r\n3)	Obtain medical care.\r\n4)	Obtain the license number, name, and personal information on everyone involved in the accident.\r\n5)	Obtain the names of witnesses to the accident.\r\n6)	Seek prompt legal assistance.\r\n\r\nIf you''ve been badly injured, your personal injury lawyer can help with interviewing witnesses, reviewing the police reports, and discussing possible settlements with insurance companies while you recover. You may not be able to do these on your own, and others may be pressing you to take a quick settlement that is not in your best interests.\r\n\r\n<h3>A personal injury attorney with our firm will look out for your best interests, both immediate and for the future.</h3>\r\n\r\nIf you are the survivor of someone who''s been sadly lost to a motorcycle accident, an experienced attorney from AziziPersonalInjury.com can evaluate the facts surrounding the accident and work with you to make sure that you receive full compensation for medical expenses, loss of income, and your pain and suffering. We are always willing to meet with you for a free, no obligation, initial compensation, and our familiarity with cases of this type will prove to be a solid and welcome help during this traumatic time, and we never charge until your case is resolved..\r\n\r\nPlease contact us as soon as possible so that we can begin helping you deal with the accident and help you begin recovering your life. You only have one chance to settle this matter with those responsible for the motorcycle accident, and we want you to receive the best possible result.', 'Motorcycle Accidents', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '142-revision-3', '', '', '2013-04-30 07:08:52', '2013-04-30 07:08:52', '', 142, 'http://azizipersonalinjury.com/dev/espanol/142-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
