dent cases. We understand how challenging it can be to work with insurance companies that want a quick settlement and do not take your short-term and long-term interests into account. We make sure we do everything possible to cover all of the details of the case and help you receive full compensation for all expenses related to the incident. \n\nContact us today for a free, no obligation consultation so that we can discuss your case. AziziPersonalInjury.com is determined to aggressively pursue your case, and we will not charge you a single dollar until the matter is fully resolved.', 'Accidentes de Peatones', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '148-autosave', '', '', '2013-05-11 02:06:57', '2013-05-11 02:06:57', '', 148, 'http://azizipersonalinjury.com/dev/espanol/148-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
