ge of by insurance companies and medical providers. \r\n\r\nYou don’t have to resort to personal loans, credit cards or other financial resources just to cover the cost of medical bills; allow our quadriplegia attorneys to assess your case and assist you with receiving adequate and fair compensation for your damages. \r\n\r\nAt AziziPersonalInjury.com, we take the time to investigate your case and aggressively litigate your claim order to build a solid case against the offending party. Contact us today for a free, no obligation consultation so that we can determine the best course of action for your quadriplegia case. We will not charge you a single dollar until your case is resolved.', 'Quadriplegia Injuries', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '150-revision-3', '', '', '2013-04-30 07:09:12', '2013-04-30 07:09:12', '', 150, 'http://azizipersonalinjury.com/dev/espanol/150-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
